git concepts
working directory -- workspace 
syaging area - prepare changes before commiting - Draft space 
Local repository - project history stored in computer 
remote repository - version of your projectr hosted on the network. allows us ot pull and push 
branches - parallel version of the projects
Pull - way to propose changes from one bracnh to other. reqwuest ti review 
merging - process of integrating changes from one branch to antoher 


git Command

git config --global user.name
git config --global user.email
git config --list


